description:
Note: This is a subset of PMP Exam Prep. If you have registered for the GreyCampus PMP Exam Prep course on Udemy, please do not register for this particular course.

A set of learning aids for the PMP (Project Management Professional) Certification Exam based on PMBoK 5 (Project Management Body of Knowledge version 5). Coverage includes

  1. A set of 25 practice questions for each of the 10 knowledge areas of PMBoK 5
  2. A set of 15 commonly used project management tool templates

BONUS CONTENT: A video on how to fill in the PMP application form

Join Today!
